name: F3009O: She-Wolf Sleeve Tunic
description:
She-Wolf Sleeve Tunic


When the full moon is out, it is a She-Wolf's playground.  Using the "Wolf-in-sheep's-skin" concept, the roles are now reversed and our Femme is using the wolf as her disguise. Coy and cunning, the She-Wolf is a force to be reckoned with.

Tinsel Korey (aka Emily Young) is a fan of the MidnightMare She-Wolf top.

100% Organic Cotton Fabric, Original Drawing, Organic Dye Solid, Water-based Screen Print, Made in Los Angeles.


Slim Fit

name: M1211O: Curse of the Wolf Crew Wash
description:
Curse of the Wolf Crew Wash


The Full Moon holds an eternal curse over the Wolf.  Bound by shackles, the Wolf is in constant battle to keep its uncontrollable alter ego from taking over.  Once transformed, the Wolf is invincible and its torturous howl continues to haunt the night.


100% Organic Cotton Fabric, Original Drawing, Specialty Wash, Water-based Screen Print, Machine Wash, Made in Los Angeles.
